{"tid":1655014,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成個連登變左做神秘台？","createTime":"2019-10-15T00:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T03:09:04.000Z","uid":86828,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0067b22048723c3c304f3441cf28c53b1d836ca5","tid":1655014,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T00:58:56.000Z","msg":"個個走去討論咩秘道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪真係要呢個時候傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪真係要開咁多個post 傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地又屌人切蛋糕時機唔啱<br />\n你地而家傾呢d野咪又係一樣唔啱時機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動post呢？ <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">民陣20號吹左雞你地又知唔知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n成日都俾人帶到風向浪費哂d時間心機傾呢d唔會有結論亦唔會完到嘅野<br />\n<br />\n未fack check嘅野又當真<br />\n又通靈又報夢<br />\n<br />\n過左成四個月個個都進步左<br />\n連傳統左膠都進步左<br />\n但我哋連登仔呢面就冇進步過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係唔可以傾，但係可唔可以諗下有冇更加有意義嘅野可以做？係咪可以推下行動post，文宣post，策略post? <br />\n<br />\n陰謀論同神秘學嘅野只會流於討論，基本上都冇方法証實，所以無論你討論得幾熱烈，對出面發生緊嘅野冇乜幫助<br />\n<br />\n你地自己諗清楚，你想連登變做612嗰日嘅大勇狀態, 定係好似而家咁日日都傾埋d唔會完到亦唔會有結論嘅野？<br />\n<br />\n無人想放棄連登呢個咁好嘅平台<br />\n但希望各位連登仔要保持智慧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足們<br />\n保持清醒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df71498b070cbba49214ea2c8a80468dd2ad57d","tid":1655014,"uid":86828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T00:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjPGd9u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjPGd9u.jpg&h=bce320eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f06da6ab6d7fd33fc6096a1fd14637d44c353328","tid":1655014,"uid":86828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:00:00.000Z","msg":"10月20民陣吹左雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd75566f48027306e3b9170aecfc9c7a192b8a2e","tid":1655014,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"集中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926f219f3eaa222f0537ec70e50354ca77a8a432","tid":1655014,"uid":25108,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"831 鬼故已經一次<br />\n今次仲勁<br />\nP牌仔開POST 咩GAY巴 勁多FANS<br />\n你話冇組織係度搞事真係冇人信"},{"pid":"fd5a35be6cbb9f30631df117003d5f7f8a1b8fac","tid":1655014,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:01:41.000Z","msg":"幫手推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 